  'The "Ben Franklin close" involves listing pros and cons with the prospect.': { prompt: 'El "cierre Ben Franklin" consiste en listar pros y contras con el prospecto.', options: ['Verdadero', 'Falso'], correctAnswer: 'Verdadero' },
